high_descs: Turn around and cross the room to face the counter between the sinks.
Open the cabinet that is second from the right, below the sinks and take the bottle out.
Turn around and face the red trash can on the floor.
Put the bottle in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a bottle in a trash can.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the door, turn left at the door, walk to the sink on the right side and look down at the cabinets below.
Open the cabinet door on the left side, take out the bottle, close the door.
Turn around and face the red bin on the floor next to the door.
Put the bottle inside of the red bin.
anns.task_desc: To move a bottle from the cabinet to the red bin.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the right sink.
Take the lotion bottle from the cabinet below the right sink.
Turn around towards the trash can.
Put the lotion bottle in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put the lotion bottle in the trash can.
